						<path
							d='M9.96291 6.70833L6.58425 3.32966L7.00016 2.91666L11.0835 7L7.00016 11.0833L6.58425 10.6703L9.96291 7.29166L2.91683 7.29166L2.91683 6.70833L9.96291 6.70833Z'
